sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant T as Telegram Interface
    participant J as Job Dispatcher
    participant W as Worker
    participant P as Provider

    U->>T: Send prompt
    T->>J: Submit run
    J-->>T: Run queued with estimate
    T-->>U: Acknowledgement
    W->>P: Execute workflow
    P-->>W: Result
    W-->>T: Final output
    T-->>U: Response